---
title: Basil Pesto & Double Bacon Risotto with Parmesan
description: Creamy, dreamy, and packed with flavour—this vibrant risotto is pure comfort in a bowl! Smokey bacon meets herbaceous pesto, with Parmesan bringing the perfect cheesy finish. Every bite is rich, savoury, and utterly irresistible. Who knew indulgence could be this easy?

